title: Hey guys, check out this boosted account.
body:
Pretty sure a 56% win rate silver 2 player with 200 games this season doesn't just miraculously learn how to play Evelynn out of nowhere and solo carry games left and right.

It amazes me how this shit doesn't get banned instantly because of how obvious it is.
